    35981:AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(oboInOwl:hasDbXref "PMID:28939894")  
  Annotation(oboInOwl:hasDbXref "PMID:31871141") Annotation(oboInOwl:hasDbXref
  "PMID:34608249") obo:IAO_0000115 obo:CL_4072104 "A chondrocyte with hybrid  
  fibroblastic-chondrogenic characteristics found in fibrocartilage,          
  particularly in the avascular inner zone and transitional middle zone of the
  meniscus. In humans, fibrochondrocytes are marked by predominant expression 
  of type I collagen (COL1A1) and fibril-associated collagens (COL3A1, COL6A1),
